What software is on our current drone? (Summary of the next 5 weeks):
OpenDroneMap but might switch back to OpenCV

What kinds of challenges/projects can YOU work on as a Software team member?
Computer vision, machine learning, also have the freedom to suggest research ideas to the leads and see what they think.

What’s the “industry standard” for drone software in 2025?
ROS 2-based for flight software, cloud stuff for data integration, etc.

How does one learn about drones effectively in 2025?
AI is often useful, but moreover just experience.
